node.areas_of_interest_freeform:
Supernode Global invests in seed stage companies building the next generation of tools and platforms that will positively shape the future of how we work, play, learn and communicate within the digital content ecosystem.

We are particularly focused on three verticals: Gaming + Interactive, Audio + Sound, Video + Visuals

We look for companies with at least some demonstrable traction and a strong value proposition.
